# Component Patterns

- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for className composition.
- Import and use `theme` from `@/lib/theme` for all surfaces, text, borders, shadows, radius, and status colors.

## Border radius

- Use `theme.radius.md` (or the literal `rounded-sm` where the file already uses raw Tailwind for layout). Never add `rounded-lg` / `rounded-xl` / `rounded-2xl` for chrome.
- Prefer `theme.patterns.inputBase`, `theme.patterns.card`, `theme.patterns.menuPanel`, and `theme.patterns.menuItem` over hand-rolled class strings.

## Shadows

- **Do not use shadows.** Remove any `shadow-*` classes. Shadows are disabled app-wide. Do not reference `theme.shadow.*`.

## Form Fields

- Border: `border-input`, `hover:border-ring`, `focus-visible:border-ring`
- Radius: `theme.radius.md` / `rounded-sm`
- Height: use `input-field-height` class for consistency

## Status Colors

- Success: `text-success`, `bg-success/10`, `border-success/60`
- Warning: `text-warning`, `bg-warning/10`, `border-warning/50`
- Error: `text-destructive`, `bg-destructive/10`, `border-destructive/50`
- Info: `text-info`, `bg-info/10`, `border-info/60`
